scope.summary:
Phase 1 is engagement-first. The EA produces text artifacts only:
(1) a draft GitHub comment for posting on OpenVINO **issue** #35641
    that links the issue to **PR** #34651 (same author, same plugin
    layer, same construct-time guard pattern) and asks Intel to
    direct the contribution shape;
(2) a CLA + AI Usage Policy compliance brief for the LA;
(3) a state report on the LA's existing OpenVINO upstream work;
(4) a Phase 1 close report.
NO code is changed. NO PR is opened. NO GitHub comment is POSTED by
the EA — the LA reviews and posts.
